WITH RegionalSales AS (
    SELECT 
        r.r_name AS region_name,
        SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_sales,
        COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS order_count
    FROM 
        region r
    JOIN 
        nation n ON r.r_regionkey = n.n_regionkey
    JOIN 
        supplier s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
    JOIN 
        partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
    JOIN 
        part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
    JOIN 
        lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
    JOIN 
        orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
    WHERE 
        o.o_orderdate >= DATE '1996-01-01' AND o.o_orderdate < DATE '1997-01-01'
    GROUP BY 
        r.r_name
),
AverageSales AS (
    SELECT 
        AVG(total_sales) AS avg_sales,
        AVG(order_count) AS avg_order_count
    FROM 
        RegionalSales
)
SELECT 
    rs.region_name,
    rs.total_sales,
    rs.order_count,
    (rs.total_sales - avg.avg_sales) / NULLIF(avg.avg_sales, 0) * 100 AS sales_variance_percentage,
    (rs.order_count - avg.avg_order_count) / NULLIF(avg.avg_order_count, 0) * 100 AS order_count_variance_percentage
FROM 
    RegionalSales rs
CROSS JOIN 
    AverageSales avg
ORDER BY 
    rs.total_sales DESC

SELECT COALESCE("t3"."REGION_NAME", "t3"."REGION_NAME") AS "REGION_NAME", "t3"."TOTAL_SALES", "t3"."ORDER_COUNT", ("t3"."TOTAL_SALES" - "t8"."AVG_SALES") / CASE WHEN "t8"."AVG_SALES" = 0.0000 THEN NULL ELSE "t8"."AVG_SALES" END * 100 AS "SALES_VARIANCE_PERCENTAGE", ("t3"."ORDER_COUNT" - "t8"."AVG_ORDER_COUNT") / CASE WHEN "t8"."AVG_ORDER_COUNT" = 0 THEN NULL ELSE "t8"."AVG_ORDER_COUNT" END * 100 AS "ORDER_COUNT_VARIANCE_PERCENTAGE"
FROM (SELECT MIN("region"."r_name") AS "REGION_NAME", SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_SALES", COUNT(DISTINCT "orders0"."o_orderkey") AS "ORDER_COUNT"
FROM "region"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "region"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "supplier"."s_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "part" ON "partsupp"."ps_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey"
INNER JOIN "orders" AS "orders0" ON "lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "orders0"."o_orderkey"
WHERE "orders0"."o_orderdate" >= DATE '1996-01-01' AND "orders0"."o_orderdate" < DATE '1997-01-01'
GROUP BY "region"."r_name") AS "t3",
(SELECT AVG(SUM("lineitem0"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem0"."l_discount"))) AS "AVG_SALES", AVG(COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."o_orderkey")) AS "AVG_ORDER_COUNT"
FROM "region" AS "region0"
INNER JOIN "nation" AS "nation0" ON "region0"."r_regionkey" = "nation0"."n_regionkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" AS "supplier0" ON "nation0"."n_nationkey" = "supplier0"."s_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" AS "partsupp0" ON "supplier0"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp0"."ps_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "part" AS "part0" ON "partsupp0"."ps_partkey" = "part0"."p_partkey"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" AS "lineitem0" ON "part0"."p_partkey" = "lineitem0"."l_partkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "lineitem0"."l_orderkey" = "s1"."o_orderkey"
WHERE "s1"."o_orderdate" >= DATE '1996-01-01' AND "s1"."o_orderdate" < DATE '1997-01-01'
GROUP BY "region0"."r_name") AS "t8"
ORDER BY "t3"."TOTAL_SALES" DESC NULLS FIRST
